seo: PHPstudy,后门漏洞,命令执行,指纹识别
summary: 该插件旨在检测phpStudy应用是否存在后门漏洞，通过发送特定请求检查是否可以利用漏洞执行命令，同时进行指纹识别确认目标系统。
summary_en: This plugin is designed to detect whether the phpStudy application has a backdoor vulnerability by sending specific requests to check if the vulnerability can be exploited to execute commands, while performing fingerprint identification to confirm the target system.
